/PGSIMH/±AT TORAH/XX656/XX/PR

/ITThe ark is opened./PR

/PR

And it happened, when the Ark began its journey,/PR


that Moses said; Arise, /SCA/XXSCENDANT /XXO/XXNE/XX,/PR

and may your enemies be scattered,/PR

and may all those who hate you/PR

run away from your light!/PR

/PR

Rise up, /SCW/XXISE /XXO/XXNE/XX, from your resting-place,/PR

you and your mighty Ark!/PR

/PR

And on that day, it shall be said:/PR

Behold, our God, for whose deliverance we hoped!/PR

This is /SCT/XXHE /XXC/XXOMPASSIONATE/XX, whom we have waited for,/PR

let us rejoice and celebrate Godòs help!/PR

/PR

Your realm endures throughout all time,/PR

your rule, throughout all generations./PR

/PR

Behold, out of Zion emerges our Torah,/PR

